{"tid":677991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應蔡政府「六四」聲明 國台辦：大陸人民才有發言權","createTime":"2018-05-25T16:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T03:10:04.000Z","uid":144372,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cd746f4c9a3b259e1b37bf64565b1b4a582873a4","tid":677991,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:22:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/2502677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F2502677&d=B3ifCGddofe07YKHAYxKP4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2c9bc39c\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/2502677</a><br />\n<br />\n適逢六四事件周年，陸委會、民進黨連發聲明，指中國大陸應省思「六四事件」重要歷史啟示，真正落實民主化及人權保障。大陸國台辦發言人馬曉光今天（6月3日）指出，大陸政治經濟社會發展情況，只有大陸人民才最有發言權。<br />\n<br />\n馬曉光回應媒體提問表示，在中國共產黨領導下，中國特色社會主義事業取得舉世矚目的成就，政治、經濟、社會、文化、生態文明建設全面推進，人民生活水準大幅改善，國際地位和影響顯著提升。我們比歷史上任何時期都更接近中華民族偉大復興的目標。"},{"pid":"b14d6d945b70d8db019a199e48ac19a184dcc394","tid":677991,"uid":9542,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:24:33.000Z","msg":"講個條友算唔算分裂罪"},{"pid":"3a4839d1c25b28ad0bc0079083d0f18c2a0b6726","tid":677991,"uid":65864,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:25:03.000Z","msg":"啱 隔籬國家嘅野都係唔好理"},{"pid":"1796cb36c66692205b3947134fe0a29edff8b232","tid":677991,"uid":117651,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:27:26.000Z","msg":"只有大陸人民才最有發言權<br />\n<br />\n但誰發言就食公安幾拳"},{"pid":"2c4dfbe70b732c813f17bd2e584759d1f4cd2eb7","tid":677991,"uid":70415,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3a4839d1c25b28ad0bc0079083d0f18c2a0b6726","tid":677991,"uid":65864,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:25:03.000Z","msg":"啱 隔籬國家嘅野都係唔好理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"正確態度，鄰國既野關我撚事，劃清界線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c01b753ad63a1dface28ce587546b69b50d4bb0","tid":677991,"uid":144372,"like":5,"dislike